><i>Find new settlements and people willing to help you.</i><br></li><li><i>Change the fate of this world or be consumed by evil.</i></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2118f08f6adb714db56c30c578186d39.poster.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2118f08f6adb714db56c30c578186d39.webm?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/2118f08f6adb714db56c30c578186d39.mp4?t=1728200973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/1347e3100d8c7f705e34efe03b468da0.avif?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=72 /></span><br><br><strong>Weak Soul</strong> tells the story of a medieval continent that has been invaded by demons. The action takes place in a post-apocalyptic dark fantasy world. Various events will be along your way to exploring the world. Don't help anyone, engage in robbery and be selfish, or increase your karma for good deeds, expecting good fortune in accomplishments.<br><br>On the way to the goal you will have to kill countless demons, die often and suffer in pain. But very few are able to endure and reach the end...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352600/extras/b2d624e483f188d4d95e5a488e254169.webp?t=1728200973\" width=618 height=48 /></span>",
